<div class="mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id="Dissections">Dissections</h3><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Regular_polygon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Dissections"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p><a href="/wiki/Coxeter" class="mw-redirect" title="Coxeter">Coxeter</a> states that every <a href="/wiki/Zonogon" title="Zonogon">zonogon</a> (a 2<i>m</i>-gon whose opposite sides are parallel and of equal length) can be dissected into <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle {\tbinom {m}{2}}}">
  <semantics>
